            <ArticleTitle>Evaluation of Brachial Plexus Using Combined Stereological Techniques of Diffusion Tensor Imaging and Fiber Tracking.</ArticleTitle>
            <Pagination>
                <MedlinePgn>e16-e23</MedlinePgn>
            </Pagination>
